title: Escape From L.A. (1996) (Kurt Russell, Stacy Keach)
description:
ESCAPE FROM L.A. - 1996

  The year is 2013. The constitution has been rewritten and the president is serving his life-long term. Red meat, along with premarital sex, alcohol and any sort of fun has been outlawed. Those who can't comply or conform are banished to Los Angeles. Unfortunately, L.A. has been isolated from the country by a devastating earthquake and transformed into a prison camp, full of the dirtiest and most uncivilized criminals and low-lifes. Snake is dispatched to this wasteland to retreive a doomsday device, hijacked by the president's daughter, which has the power to revert Earth back to the dark ages.

  Starring: Kurt Russell, A.J. Langer, Steve Buscemi, Georges Corraface, Stacy Keach, Bruce Campbell, Peter Fonda, Pam Grier.

  Directed by: John Carpenter.

  Length: 1hr. 41min.
